General Information

Immediate relief from pain and soreness between toes. Prevents pressure and rubbing.

Scholl Toe Separators provide relief from pain and soreness between the toes.



  • The soft foam cushions and protects tender areas.

  • Ideal for sore toes, blisters and corns between the toes.

  • Washable.

  • Immediate relief from pain and soreness between toes.

  • Prevents pressure and rubbing.


Place between toes with the longer side uppermost.


2 Large 1 Small.

Boxed Contents: 2 Large, 1 Small Toe Separators

Size: 1 Pack

Warnings

KEEP OUT THE REACH OF CHILDREN.

ESSENTIAL SAFETY INFORMATION

Please SEEK ADVICE before use if you have diabetes as your foot condition may require treatment by a healthcare professional.

Directions

Place between toes with the longer side uppermost. Washing instructions: Hand wash with mild soap and lukewarm water. Rinse thoroughly then leave to dry naturally.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place out of direct sunlight.
